matter is how...

10
00:00:52,208 --> 00:00:56,416
I want... I really want
to hold Master's hand.

11
00:02:26,625 --> 00:02:29,291
Culture. The Age of
Exploration heralded the start

12
00:02:29,375 --> 00:02:31,625
of a new age
of cultural trade.

13
