During this era... the
Europeans became aware of

14
00:02:36,333 --> 00:02:39,958
countless other peoples
and cultures. Of course...

15
00:02:40,041 --> 00:02:42,791
they viewed the inhabitants
of the Americas as savages,

16
00:02:42,875 --> 00:02:45,333
but they were fascinated by
the enormity of their culture

17
00:02:45,416 --> 00:02:47,166
