ya know, stuff like that.

31
00:03:33,208 --> 00:03:34,416
Oh.

32
00:03:39,208 --> 00:03:41,916
Master, will you be
taking part in the fair too?

33
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,750
No... it's a pain in my
ass... Only way I would is if

34
00:03:44,833 --> 00:03:47,416
my class forced me to join.
Way I see it, I'm not in

